descriptionHTML:
Android Wear 5.0 watch faces.

By installing this app you get beautiful and elegant watch face designs for your android wear device.
Use this app to configure custom settings for each watch face.

To use a watch face:
1. Hold down on your current Android Wear Smart Watch watch face until watch face selector menu shows up
2. Swipe to TechWear watch face
3. Tap to select as your new watch face

To change settings for current watch face:
1. Open TechWear App on your mobile phone
2. Tap on currently selected watch face
3. Once the setting page opens modify any settings you wish
4. Settings will be applied to watch face when not in ambient mode


More watch faces coming soon...
